Chapter#    Description
1           Gates are implemented from the ground up.
2           Various higher level combinatorial chips implemented.
3           Timers and basic sequential chips.
4           (empty) Exploratory chapter for Hack assembly code.
5           Final pieces of the virtual hardware implemented. Top most "chip"
            is the PC, which includes a Screen and an Input device.

